Package org.example.view.gui.utilities

Class ImageCard

java.lang.Object
org.example.view.gui.utilities.ImageCard
public class ImageCard extends Object
The ImageCard class represents a card with an image and interactive corner buttons. This class handles the display of the card and interactions with its corners.
